    "name": {
      "zh": "WARTECH TV-109 + TV-106 胸挂（A-TACS 橄榄绿迷彩）",
      "en": "WARTECH TV-109 + TV-106 chest rig (A-TACS FG)"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "WT胸挂",
      "en": "TV-106 + TV-109"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "WARTECH 复合胸挂系统由 TV-106 野战武装带以及 TV-109 重型悬挂系统组成。装具肩带填充有泡沫补强整体结构，还设有 MOLLE 系统绑带用于扩展额外功能。将 TV-106 与 TV-109 组合到一起后，整套装具就成了功能齐全的战术胸挂系统。",
      "en": "The WARTECH gear rig consisting of the TV-106 Battle Belt and TV-109 heavy suspension system. The shoulder straps are reinforced with foam and have MOLLE straps, and the TV-109 combined with the TV-106 completes the belt system into a full-featured gear rig."
    },
